@startuml LoginUserAltWrongCredentials
title UC 2.1.2 - Prijava (Alt: Netačni kredencijali)

actor "Registrovani korisnik" as U
participant "Frontend (React)" as FE
participant "Backend API (Express)" as BE
database "MySQL" as DB

U -> FE: Unosi email i lozinku
U -> FE: Klik na "Prijavi se"
FE -> BE: POST /auth/login
BE -> DB: Dohvata korisnika po emailu
DB --> BE: Podaci o korisniku / ili null
BE -> BE: Provera lozinke (ili korisnik ne postoji)
BE --> FE: 401 Unauthorized
FE -> U: Prikaz poruke o grešci
@enduml